snippet.textDisplay:
Not a blockbuster movie trailer in the 2010's if it doesn't start with a bass shaking beat followed by quiet piano note in the background with a string crescendo and electric guitar riff to build up the tension. Feel the edge. Feel the lack of creativity! Feel the lack of soul!


Also, sniff sniff can't you just smell that corporate appeasement? If this movie had come out years ago we would have eaten it up in a heartbeat. But noooooo, Disney didn't think a girl movie outside of their usual princess schlock would be a success, much less a girl superhero movie. . . At least they took their heads out of their asses long enough to smell the money in our wallets. Corporate pigs!
